AudioData.Text: Welcome to the demo scene for the track and measure add-on for VR Builder. Teleport to a station to check out some of the add-on's features.
Build a pyramid with the cubes. The timer will start when you grab the first cube. You can reset the table at any time by pressing that inconspicuous red button.
It was a good performance, but you can do better.
You sure took your time! Next time, try to bring out your inner toddler.
You can reset the table to try again.
Congratulations! You managed to trigger the line for the longest time threshold. You did this on purpose, right?
That wasn't too hard, was it?
Acting randomly would have yielded a better score. Did you deliberately choose to fail?
You can do better. Why not try again?
Push the button corresponding to the color of the cube.
Not to hurt your feelings, but are you sure you got the instructions right?
